                "invention-title": [
                    "Sensitive electrode for non-preenrichment electrochemical detection of heavy metal ions in water, preparation method and application thereof",
                    "一种无预富集电化学检测水中重金属离子的敏感电极、制备方法及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a non-preenrichment sensitive electrode for electrochemically detecting heavy metal ions in water, a preparation method and application of the non-preenrichment sensitive electrode in the aspect of detecting the heavy metal ions in the water, and belongs to the technical field of electrochemical sensing. The method comprises the following steps: firstly, cleaning carbon cloth, then carrying out electrochemical deposition by taking a mixed solution of sodium tungstate, sodium molybdate, perchloric acid and hydrogen peroxide as a deposition solution, the carbon cloth as a working electrode, a platinum sheet as a counter electrode and an Ag/AgCl electrode as a reference electrode, and cleaning to obtain the molybdenum-doped tungsten oxide sensitive electrode. And detecting cadmium ions, lead ions, copper ions and mercury ions by taking the cadmium ions, the lead ions, the copper ions and the mercury ions as a working electrode, a platinum sheet as a counter electrode and a saturated calomel electrode as a reference electrode. The sensitive electrode successfully prepared through an electrochemical technology has the advantages of being direct, efficient, good in electrochemical detection capacity, high in sensitivity, wide in linear detection range, low in detection limit, good in stability, good in repeatability and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种无预富集电化学检测水中重金属离子的敏感电极、制备方法及其在检测水中重金属离子方面的应用，属于电化学传感技术领域。本发明首先对碳布进行清洗，然后以钨酸钠、钼酸钠、高氯酸和过氧化氢的混合溶液作为沉积液，以碳布为工作电极、铂片为对电极、Ag/AgCl电极为参比电极，进行电化学沉积，清洗后得到钼掺杂氧化钨敏感电极；再以其为工作电极、铂片为对电极、饱和甘汞电极为参比电极，对镉离子、铅离子、铜离子、汞离子进行检测。本发明通过电化学技术成功地制备的敏感电极，具有直接高效的特点，而且电化学检测能力良好，具有较高的灵敏度、较宽的线性检测范围和较低的检出限，此外该敏感电极还具有稳定性好、重复性好等优点。"
                }
            ]
